Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.63,0:01:52.55,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,维拉尔大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.77,0:02:14.48,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,提欧・科尔内罗伯爵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.94,0:02:17.82,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,再次献上我的圣印的时刻到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.49,0:02:22.78,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,前提是大家没有异议
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.08,0:02:26.58,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能有异议
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.87,0:02:30.58,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,西斯迪纳公配得上这个位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.79,0:02:32.84,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,已是有目共睹的事实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.13,0:02:35.55,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我也申请从属
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.92,0:02:38.93,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想从属于提欧阁下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.59,0:02:44.68,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  我想舍弃康斯坦斯的姓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.10,0:02:47.89,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,改用母亲的姓斯蒂利亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.18,0:02:49.39,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,请等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.56,0:02:52.48,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有兄长维拉尔的器量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.86,0:02:56.15,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这座城被米尔扎夺走时也一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.36,0:02:58.82,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我非但没帮上兄长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.24,0:03:00.91,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,到头来只是在扯后腿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.16,0:03:02.41,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.29,0:03:10.17,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你更配继承康斯坦斯家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.92,0:03:11.88,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  从今天开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.46,0:03:15.17,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是康斯坦斯家的家主了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.71,0:03:19.01,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.55,0:03:23.60,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,然后  你也从属于提欧•科尔内罗阁下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.60,0:03:26.64,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟把我俩的爵位加起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.10,0:03:30.44,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,也不够格统治阿尔图克和莱加里亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.10,0:03:33.73,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,只要提欧大人愿意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.48,0:03:36.57,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我接受了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.32,0:03:48.58,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  我的主人  西斯迪纳公提欧•科尔内罗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.62,0:03:50.12,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,成为条约的盟主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.71,0:03:55.21,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,并保管诸位的圣印  没问题吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.77,0:04:18.02,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我打算继承为保护我们而牺牲的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.78,0:04:21.86,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,维拉尔・康斯坦斯伯爵的意志
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.78,0:04:27.66,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,维拉尔大人遵守了联合的与同盟和解的决议
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.16,0:04:30.45,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望我们也能朝这个目标努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.70,0:04:34.17,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔图克条细将从中立的立场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.04,0:04:36.79,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,从联合独立
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.46,0:04:43.05,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦我们独立  了想必联合会更加动摇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.26,0:04:45.89,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,很难想象同盟会同意和解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.22,0:04:49.60,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就结果而言  岂不是帮了同盟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.81,0:04:52.64,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就跟往常一样 既要帮助联合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.02,0:04:54.77,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,也要跟同盟继续战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.35,0:04:58.82,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我们追求的目标始终是三阵营的力量均衡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.44,0:05:01.36,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,令战斗变得胶着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.65,0:05:04.24,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,否则是没法谈判的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.95,0:05:08.20,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说只能期待联合啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.32,0:05:11.79,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 如果联合没有行动就无法继续下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.66,0:05:15.87,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然杀死米尔扎太子并夺回了阿尔图克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.46,0:05:18.21,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,但同盟仍旧很强大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.92,0:05:21.55,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,很遗憾  我们没时间慢慢来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.05,0:05:27.26,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  今晚就好好为获胜庆祝吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.62,0:06:32.74,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这下真累了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.71,0:06:41.33,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.79,0:06:42.63,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,提欧大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.38,0:06:46.84,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,您还没休息吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.09,0:06:47.38,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.80,0:06:48.72,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,想必很累吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.05,0:06:50.68,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,请去休息吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.01,0:06:53.51,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我是打算休息  只不过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.72,0:06:56.27,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我想先跟你聊聊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.52,0:06:56.93,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.73,0:07:04.23,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,请用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.69,0:07:05.32,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.74,0:07:19.62,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜您当上阿尔图克条约的盟主及伯爵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.46,0:07:22.58,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我明显不够格啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.67,0:07:24.84,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,您表现得已经很坦然了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.04,0:07:27.51,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,在宴会上也没有摆架子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.63,0:07:31.43,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,反而顾及了诸位公爵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.88,0:07:34.26,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这很像提欧大人的作风
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.10,0:07:35.60,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.64,0:07:37.06,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,被他们认同我就放心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.93,0:07:41.02,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,士兵和民众的人气也非常了得啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.77,0:07:43.44,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,只要提欧大人现身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.73,0:07:45.98,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,每个人都会用欢声迎接
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.82,0:07:49.53,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,明明在这场战争中也让众多士兵阵亡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.40,0:07:52.70,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,还让民众付出了牺牲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.70,0:07:54.49,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,说实话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.12,0:07:56.20,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我很心痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.70,0:07:59.75,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,请不要忘记这种心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.04,0:08:03.21,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,时刻不忘为人民着想的统治
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.62,0:08:05.67,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,当然  我绝不会忘记
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.34,0:08:09.71,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,但我最终的梦想依然跟过去一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.96,0:08:13.38,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,即回到故乡马尔扎  让村子过上幸福生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.59,0:08:14.01,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.80,0:08:19.22,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不对  只有一点跟那时不一样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.73,0:08:21.77,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.35,0:08:23.77,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是最后的梦想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.40,0:08:26.73,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,希望回到马尔扎的我身边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.02,0:08:28.19,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,有你陪伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.44,0:08:31.49,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,遇上提欧大人的那一刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.65,0:08:33.57,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我便发誓会永远忠于您
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.82,0:08:36.37,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不用说  我打算终生为您效劳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.66,0:08:40.37,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉又没有成功表达岀来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.41,0:08:40.83,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.71,0:08:50.00,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,相爱的二人理应结合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.38,0:08:54.72,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,并非只适用于艾莱克西斯大人和马丽娜大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.01,0:08:57.47,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这很重要…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.60,0:09:01.10,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,请说得严谨一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.39,0:09:05.14,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我回马尔扎的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.06,0:09:08.23,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你不是以契约魔法师的身份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.36,0:09:11.44,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,而是以妃子的身份陪伴着我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.69,0:09:16.16,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,一直以来  我刻意不去想这件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.53,0:09:19.62,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,只要能跟提欧大人做着同样的梦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.99,0:09:21.24,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我就很幸福了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.58,0:09:23.87,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,在独处的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.37,0:09:26.79,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,像这样温柔待我也让我很幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.12,0:09:29.38,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,而且  以提欧大人目前的条件来说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.63,0:09:32.38,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,能挑到数不尽的好女人为妃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.55,0:09:35.63,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,除你之外  我无法想象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.26,0:09:38.47,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是想讲明这点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.64,0:09:49.23,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此那我现在就成为提欧大人的妃子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.56,0:09:54.49,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  可以等实现目标之后再对外宣布吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.82,0:09:55.99,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我不介意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.36,0:09:59.28,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,因为重要的是我们的感情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.66,0:10:03.62,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,还有  我有一个请求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.00,0:10:04.66,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.08,0:10:10.08,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,请不要比我先死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.09,0:10:16.22,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,世界充满了混沌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.92,0:10:19.47,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,现在是乱世  而我是君主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.39,0:10:23.43,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,今后还要跟强大的敌人战斗呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.35,0:10:25.31,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那也不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.43,0:10:27.94,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我无法信守承诺呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.48,0:10:30.06,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我也会死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.40,0:10:33.27,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那我的责任就大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.61,0:10:39.78,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,条约的盟主已确定是提欧•科尔内罗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.87,0:10:44.58,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这下条约的团结就更坚固了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.16,0:10:48.04,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,卢克莱尔伯爵的情况如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.29,0:10:51.13,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟与阿尔图克伯爵的关系很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.79,0:10:54.63,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,跟条约联手的可能性很高吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.09,0:10:56.96,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那可是难缠的对手啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.38,0:11:01.97,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,无论如何都要避免他们跟条约共同攻打我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.18,0:11:04.93,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那个谈判怎样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.47,0:11:08.02,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,有报告称很顺利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.06,0:11:10.90,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那就替我传个话  尽快实施作战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.06,0:11:11.44,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.65,0:11:14.32,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,只要拿下卢克莱尔伯爵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.65,0:11:16.98,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就能重创联合的战斗力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.49,0:11:18.94,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,一鼓作气分出胜负吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.29,0:11:29.37,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,长得很好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.75,0:11:30.29,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,普莉希拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.08,0:11:31.54,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.17,0:11:34.04,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,方便吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.13,0:11:39.38,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.18,0:11:45.89,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,前些国子圣印教团的教皇雷欧涅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.39,0:11:49.10,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎宣称自己才是圣杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.48,0:11:50.60,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.89,0:11:53.90,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  真正的圣杯是你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.44,0:11:58.15,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我生下来就获得了圣印
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.82,0:12:03.16,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我的圣印确实是那种形状
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.70,0:12:06.99,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲也说我就是圣杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.87,0:12:14.58,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 信徒之中也有人将我称作法尔内塞的圣杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.92,0:12:16.38,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你的父亲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.09,0:12:21.13,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是圣印教团的教主埃内斯托•法尔内塞对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.38,0:12:21.84,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.43,0:12:25.55,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,圣杯到底是什么东西啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.59,0:12:27.05,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,圣印教团内部的教诲是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.35,0:12:29.89,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,只要全世界的圣印集中到圣杯中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.47,0:12:31.98,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就能召唤出消除混沌的神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.23,0:12:34.19,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,跟皇帝圣印差不多啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.56,0:12:38.40,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 既然你被叫作圣杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.57,0:12:44.41,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,对教皇而言  你应该是碍事的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.95,0:12:48.28,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那位大人的话  也许会这么想吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.91,0:12:52.54,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,搞不好教皇企图加害于你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.96,0:12:53.71,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.50,0:12:56.63,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,提欧大人也要当心哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.75,0:12:59.92,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,既然已经宣称自己是圣杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.09,0:13:02.47,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是在表明自己有意搜集圣印
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.76,0:13:04.76,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说  提欧大人的圣印
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.88,0:13:06.80,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,也有很大概率被盯上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.26,0:13:08.26,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.55,0:13:12.73,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,话说  西露卡现在是怎么看圣印教团的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.98,0:13:19.15,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是认为教团的教诲和圣杯是自圆其说的鬼话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.28,0:13:23.65,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  我之所以能当上条约的盟主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.11,0:13:26.53,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,也许是因为唯一神的指引呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.99,0:13:29.66,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这是因前提欧大人的努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.08,0:13:34.21,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,无论如何都不能把圣印献给教团哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.46,0:13:38.96,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道呢  如果这个圣印能拯救你和大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.25,0:13:40.92,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是会毫不犹豫地献出的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.55,0:13:43.46,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,西露卡大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.59,0:13:44.47,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,有报告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.10,0:13:56.02,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,有报告称 卢克莱尔伯爵客鲁特•凯拉斯大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.56,0:14:02.53,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,在与瓦尔林德军的战斗中壮烈牺牲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.57,0:14:05.90,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,克鲁特阁下…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.61,0:14:08.99,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,在我方援军抵达前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.32,0:14:12.87,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,遭到道森公派出的佣兵援军背叛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.20,0:14:14.25,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.29,0:14:16.25,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,道森公后来怎样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.75,0:14:18.92,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,据说投靠同盟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.25,0:14:22.67,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,道森公果然与敌人暗中勾结了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.25,0:14:24.34,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,看来是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.84,0:14:27.47,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,听说他召集了来往密切的联合君主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.72,0:14:29.80,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,号召他们从属
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.18,0:14:32.47,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,受到号召的君主们的反应呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.72,0:14:35.64,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎暂时还没有响应的君主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.77,0:14:36.23,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.27,0:14:40.19,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过联合失去了卢克莱尔伯爵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.44,0:14:42.48,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,处境愈发严峻了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.69,0:14:45.57,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不如愿是常有的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.82,0:14:48.11,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,重要的是该如何平息事态
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.86,0:14:50.07,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你有什么主意吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.53,0:14:52.70,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这倒是算不上主意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.91,0:14:55.04,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要两个人一起去哈鲁西亚啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.45,0:14:57.37,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒是无所谓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.29,0:15:00.75,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,条约已经从联合独立了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.25,0:15:04.84,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,也许在对方看来 我们就是叛徒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.84,0:15:08.01,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这就只能相信阿莱克希斯大人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.17,0:15:13.26,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,悲报连连 哈鲁西亚公现在肯定很失落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.51,0:15:15.47,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,提欧大人可是他的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.60,0:15:17.47,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,请去鼓励一下他吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.06,0:15:19.18,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,鼓励…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.56,0:15:21.27,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,如今卢克莱尔伯爵已战死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.56,0:15:23.23,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,能拯救联合绝境的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.56,0:15:25.36,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就只剩下阿莱克希斯大人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.28,0:15:27.74,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,只要他能站超来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.24,0:15:29.82,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,其余诸国也会接连奋起吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.37,0:15:37.08,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.45,0:15:38.87,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,铁甲船啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.16,0:15:43.58,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得 应该是子爵级的爵位报酬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.96,0:15:47.55,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,貌似是前大公用多余的爵位换来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.21,0:15:51.68,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过据说船速太慢  根本没有实用性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.30,0:15:54.60,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,由于是无法与敌人战斗的军舰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.93,0:15:57.72,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,在当地被称为无敌舰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.06,0:16:00.23,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,威严感倒是非比寻常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.73,0:16:03.85,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.81,0:16:07.78,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,阿莱克希斯大人说非常愿意见面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.28,0:16:09.36,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.70,0:16:15.74,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我听说了你的活跃表现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.16,0:16:19.50,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,简直就像始祖君主莱恩的传说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.62,0:16:24.79,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这是以在此的西露卡为首的同伴们的功劳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.50,0:16:28.55,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你当上阿尔图克条约的盟主了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.84,0:16:29.30,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.13,0:16:32.30,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,然后从联合独立了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.09,0:16:34.84,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能重新考虑呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.14,0:16:38.85,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我能依靠的就只有你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.06,0:16:41.89,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,反倒希望你来当联合的盟主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.40,0:16:45.52,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我无法接受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.90,0:16:49.48,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我的愿望是让同盟和联合和解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.40,0:16:51.24,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,和解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.24,0:16:55.49,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪我执着于和解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.66,0:16:57.83,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,才失去了阿尔图克伯爵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.41,0:17:01.50,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,当时我若是选择与同盟开战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.70,0:17:05.79,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,想必联合就不会沦落至此吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.50,0:17:07.71,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,也许吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.00,0:17:11.80,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 阿莱克希斯大人失去了更重要事物吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.26,0:17:14.30,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,马丽娜…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.55,0:17:18.22,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,即便联合打倒了同盟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.01,0:17:20.81,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,没有马丽娜的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.93,0:17:22.81,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,对阿莱克希斯大人而言应该毫无意义才对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.35,0:17:25.02,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,对我而言确实如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.35,0:17:27.35,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我寻求与同盟和解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.61,0:17:30.77,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  马丽娜不一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.53,0:17:36.70,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,因为马丽娜大人认为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.91,0:17:43.20,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,必须用武力统一圣印  让皇帝圣印诞生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.79,0:17:46.08,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,明明只要我跟马丽娜结婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.62,0:17:49.42,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,圣印终究会统一？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.67,0:17:52.00,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,因为有人不愿看见这一幕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.13,0:17:54.42,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,所以发生了那场惨剧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.76,0:17:55.34,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.88,0:17:58.59,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,从那天开始一切都改变了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.85,0:18:03.22,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我想否定那场惨剧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.56,0:18:06.10,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我想夺回那个事件发生前的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.27,0:18:10.77,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,当然 我也希望如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.15,0:18:13.69,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,但事到如今 我不认为能办到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.07,0:18:14.86,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,能办到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.90,0:18:19.24,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,为此  必须让联合  同盟及条约这三股势力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.66,0:18:22.16,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,在军事上保持均势
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.53,0:18:24.29,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,联合哪来的这个力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.45,0:18:25.45,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,有的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.75,0:18:28.17,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,联合诸国经济上很富裕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.46,0:18:32.00,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,至今没有战争  没有人员上的损耗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.46,0:18:36.22,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,反倒是战事不断的同盟应该处于水深火热中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.55,0:18:38.18,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,只要阿莱克希斯大人站起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.26,0:18:39.05,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,—定…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.55,0:18:42.89,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我办不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.14,0:18:49.31,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,哪怕这是为了拯救马丽娜大人吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.23,0:18:51.36,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,拯救她？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.36,0:18:53.86,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么意思呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.27,0:18:58.20,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,即便用武力统一圣印  当上皇帝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.53,0:19:00.36,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,她也绝不可能获得幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.45,0:19:02.74,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这太奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.08,0:19:04.74,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,马丽娜是凭自身意志…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.16,0:19:08.21,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,她无非是压抑了自己的感情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.46,0:19:11.67,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,想履行同盟盟主的义务
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.71,0:19:14.34,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,可是  我不认为这很伟大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.34,0:19:17.38,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,因为如果伪装着自己的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.76,0:19:19.72,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那无论有怎样的成就都没意义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.84,0:19:25.81,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我无法容忍马丽娜大人封闭自己的心不断战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.27,0:19:29.43,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,她明明爱着阿莱克希斯大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.69,0:19:31.06,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这是真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.27,0:19:31.73,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.44,0:19:35.90,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,马丽娜大人如今仍爱着阿莱克希斯大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.57,0:19:42.20,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这是干真万确的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.28,0:19:46.95,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,能阻止马丽娜大人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.12,0:19:48.37,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就只有您
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.62,0:19:54.46,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我决定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.00,0:19:57.17,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,决定什么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.63,0:20:00.26,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,决定成为你的妃子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.75,0:20:32.50,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,阿莱克希斯大人  您要去哪里啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.92,0:20:35.25,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我接下来要去讨伐道森公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.46,0:20:38.42,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,您刚才说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.30,0:20:40.46,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,阿莱克希斯大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.97,0:20:44.64,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,立刻准备出征
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.35,0:20:50.47,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,阿莱克希斯大人出战了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.64,0:20:51.89,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这才醒悟啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.52,0:20:53.52,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  有意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.81,0:20:55.44,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也去大闹一场吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.94,0:20:57.94,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,跟着阿莱克希斯大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.53,0:21:07.28,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,卢克莱尔的小子也不值一提啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.41,0:21:08.24,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.37,0:21:11.25,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,联合那帮人以德赛那毛孩为首
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.29,0:21:15.37,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,也是一群没有远见的胆小蠢 货没错吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.46,0:21:17.13,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,所言极是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.26,0:21:25.26,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.55,0:21:29.26,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,哈鲁西亚公正率大军逼近这座城
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.43,0:21:30.26,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.28,0:21:51.58,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直以为一旦同盟获胜  马丽娜当上皇帝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.74,0:21:53.87,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就能带来更好的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.45,0:21:57.17,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 如果说这样会让她受伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.96,0:22:00.92,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那我…
